      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>cucumber</strong> into discs</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining cucumber</strong> in half lengthways, scrape out the inner seeds with a teaspoon and discard</p><p>Grate the <strong>deseeded cucumber</strong> and squeeze out any excess water</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> roughly</p>",
