    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cucumber discs</strong>, <strong>chopped tomato</strong> and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>sliced shallot </strong>to a bowl with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> and a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>cucumber & tomato salad</strong></p>",
