    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>grated cucumber</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>remaining grated garlic</strong>, your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong>, a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>tzatziki</strong></p><p>When the chicken and chips are almost ready, add your <strong>sourdough pitta[s] </strong>to the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through, then slice in half</p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
